// src/icons.js
import { library } from "@fortawesome/fontawesome-svg-core";
import {
  faHome,
  faUser,
  faSearch,
  faBell,
  faComments,
  faUsers,
  faCalendar,
  faShoppingBag,
  faCog,
  faQuestionCircle,
  faSignOutAlt,
} from "@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons";

// Add icons to the library
library.add(
  faHome,
  faUser,
  faSearch,
  faBell,
  faComments,
  faUsers,
  faCalendar,
  faShoppingBag,
  faCog,
  faQuestionCircle,
  faSignOutAlt
);
